10.Work with filter commands on date.

syntax:sort (filename)
It is used to displays the date in sorted order.
for ascending -d,descending -r,numerical -n
output:
[24bcs105@mepcolinux linux]$sort -d f1.txt
apr
feb
jan
mar
[24bcs105@mepcolinux linux]$sort -r f1.txt
mar
jan
feb
apr

11.Create a compressed file archieve using tar commands.

Synatx:tar -cvzf archieve.tar filename
It creates a compressed file archieve using tar commands.
output:
[24bcs105@mepcolinux linux]$tar -cvzf 2025.tar.gz linux1
linux1/

12.Extract files from archieve tar.

Syntax:tar -xvzf archieve.tar
It extracts files from archieve tar.
output:
[24bcs105@mepcolinux linux]$tar -xvzf 2025.tar.gz
linux1/
[24bcs105@mepcolinux linux]$ls
2025.tar.gz  exp1.prn  exp2.prn  f1.txt  linux1
